  <brief_title>An Open Label, Randomized, Crossover Study To Estimate The Pharmacokinetics And Evaluate The Safety Following A Single Dose Of Azithromycin 2g Extended-Release Powder For Oral Suspension With A 3-Day Dosing Regimen Of Azithromycin 500mg Tablet In Chinese Healthy Male Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Open Label, Randomized, Crossover Study To Estimate The Pharmacokinetics And Evaluate The Safety Following A Single Dose Of Azithromycin 2g Extended-Release Powder For Oral Suspension With A 3-Day Dosing Regimen Of Azithromycin 500mg Tablet In Chinese Healthy Male Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
