  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to estimate the pharmacokinetics and evaluate the safety
      following a single dose of azithromycin 2g extended-release powder for oral suspension with a
      3-day dosing regimen of azithromycin 500mg tablet in Chinese healthy male subjects. This
      study data will be used to support azithromycin NDA in China.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
